[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1242},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20210929\u002F585008686\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20210929\u002F585008686\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20210929\u002F585008686\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20210929\u002F585008686\u002F":1221,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20210929\u002F585008686\u002F":1230},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F29\u002Fpython-from-js-28-closures\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1204,"date":1205,"description":18,"extension":1206,"lang":1207,"meta":1208,"navigation":51,"path":1209,"readingMinutes":1210,"seo":1211,"standalone":1212,"stem":1213,"tags":1214,"tldr":1218,"updated":1218,"url":1219,"__hash__":1220},"content\u002F從 JavaScript 角度學 Python\u002F從-JavaScript-角度學-Python-28-閉包-Closure.md","從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(28) - 閉包(Closure)","585008686",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1195},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,28,76,87,118,121,128,131,135,138,278,295,298,352,355,397,404,407,410,413,915,918,1109,1112,1115,1121,1124,1140,1143,1146,1149,1152,1185,1191],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"那 JavaScript 中有一個東西叫做閉包 (Closure)，Python 也會有嗎？所以這章節就輕鬆的聊一下如果你想要在 Python 中寫閉包的話該如何撰寫。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"變數作用域",[16,23,24],{},"首先先簡單回顧聊一下前面的「從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(6) - 變數作用域」章節，我們都知道每一個變數都有屬於它自己的作用域，例如：全域變數、區域變數等等。",[16,26,27],{},"那麼如果拿全域變數來講的話，你只要放在程式碼的最外層，就一定可以透過類似 JavaScript 的範圍鍊概念向上尋找到變數：",[29,30,35],"pre",{"className":31,"code":32,"language":33,"meta":34,"style":34},"language-py shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","money = 1\n\ndef fn():\n  print(money) # 1\n\nfn()\n","py","",[36,37,38,46,53,59,65,70],"code",{"__ignoreMap":34},[39,40,43],"span",{"class":41,"line":42},"line",1,[39,44,45],{},"money = 1\n",[39,47,49],{"class":41,"line":48},2,[39,50,52],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":51},true,"\n",[39,54,56],{"class":41,"line":55},3,[39,57,58],{},"def fn():\n",[39,60,62],{"class":41,"line":61},4,[39,63,64],{},"  print(money) # 1\n",[39,66,68],{"class":41,"line":67},5,[39,69,52],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":51},[39,71,73],{"class":41,"line":72},6,[39,74,75],{},"fn()\n",[16,77,78,79,82,83,86],{},"至於區域變數呢？前面都有說過 Python 的變數類似 JavaScript 的 ",[36,80,81],{},"var"," 變數，因此會是以 ",[36,84,85],{},"function"," 為作用域，因此宣告在函式內的變數我們就無法在這個函式之外取得：",[29,88,90],{"className":31,"code":89,"language":33,"meta":34,"style":34},"def fn():\n  money = 1\n  print(money) # 1\n\nfn()\nprint(money) # NameError: name 'money' is not defined\n",[36,91,92,96,101,105,109,113],{"__ignoreMap":34},[39,93,94],{"class":41,"line":42},[39,95,58],{},[39,97,98],{"class":41,"line":48},[39,99,100],{},"  money = 1\n",[39,102,103],{"class":41,"line":55},[39,104,64],{},[39,106,107],{"class":41,"line":61},[39,108,52],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":51},[39,110,111],{"class":41,"line":67},[39,112,75],{},[39,114,115],{"class":41,"line":72},[39,116,117],{},"print(money) # NameError: name 'money' is not defined\n",[16,119,120],{},"好的，我們複習差不多了，今天大概就到這邊...",[16,122,123],{},[124,125],"img",{"alt":126,"src":127},"再騙我啊！","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FPython\u002F%E5%BE%9E%20JavaScript%20%E8%A7%92%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%B8%20Python\u002F1632558615063.png",[16,129,130],{},"別急，我們只是快速複習一下變數作用域的部分，接下來就讓我們準備了解 Python 的閉包該怎麼寫吧。",[12,132,134],{"id":133},"閉包closure","閉包(Closure)",[16,136,137],{},"那麼在了解並開始撰寫 Python 閉包之前，讓我先擷取我先前寫的 JavaScript 閉包範例程式碼：",[29,139,143],{"className":140,"code":141,"language":142,"meta":34,"style":34},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","function count() {\n let icash = 1000;\n return function (price){\n  icash = icash - price;\n  return icash;\n }\n}\nlet ray = count();\nray(100); \u002F\u002F 900\nray(200); \u002F\u002F 700\n","js",[36,144,145,158,176,194,209,217,222,228,244,263],{"__ignoreMap":34},[39,146,147,150,154],{"class":41,"line":42},[39,148,85],{"class":149},"sOudu",[39,151,153],{"class":152},"scAaK"," count",[39,155,157],{"class":156},"s8XSl","() {\n"